### 5. Invalid Request - Missing Required Fields (Should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/form/submit-json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "email": "invalid-test@example.com"
}

###

### 6. Invalid Request - Invalid Email (Should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/form/submit-json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "interests": ["Website Development"],
  "budget": "$5,000 - $10,000",
  "newsletterSubscribed": true,
  "privacyPolicyAccepted": true
}

